{"id":258045,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-无锡上访维权者丁红芬被关黑监狱111日，体/","date":"2012-10-19T09:16:11Z","modified":"2012-10-19T09:16:11Z","title":"维权网 | 无锡上访维权者丁红芬被关黑监狱111日，体重降30斤（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，江苏无锡访民丁红芬等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>多位被强拆的上访户在北京国家信访局反映政府腐败问题，被无锡政府截回关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，丁红芬在被当地所谓法制教育学习班剥夺人身自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span><span>天以后，从黑监狱释放回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>关押期间，丁红芬受到非人的折磨，体重从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">140</span><span>斤饿瘦到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">114</span><span>斤。有三十多天，丁红芬每天只有一两食物，不给盐吃，丁红芬连水都喝不下，身上所有的血管全部瘪掉，下肢发凉，看守向上级汇报后，丁红芬才吃上了馒头咸菜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丁红芬回家第一个看到的是父亲，老人家呆呆的含着泪，丁红芬也呆了，父亲头发一下子全白了，父亲说，以为见不到了丁红芬</span><span> </span><span>，摸着丁红芬，说活着回家就好。当地百姓们听说了丁红芬的遭遇，纷纷前往看望。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丁红芬已经向警察报案，要追究非法限制公民人身自由的法制教育学习班参与者的法律责任。丁红芬表示，要继续维权，不信正不压邪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vAZpx7w-pns/UIDNIfQ1mOI/AAAAAAAARcs/RL6ONgUx-34/s1600/11.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vAZpx7w-pns/UIDNIfQ1mOI/AAAAAAAARcs/RL6ONgUx-34/s320/11.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-3IP-NRpUYH4/UIDNOgTjTUI/AAAAAAAARc0/vkfJETlPKaw/s1600/12.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-3IP-NRpUYH4/UIDNOgTjTUI/AAAAAAAARc0/vkfJETlPKaw/s320/12.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>相关报道请参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/09/83.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/09/83.html</a></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2751641088242554344?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}